ive Pro kit includes motion controllers, a high-resolution VR display, and everything else you need to turn your PC into a VR gaming rig. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-317001" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/HTC-Vive-Pro-Kit.jpg" alt="HTC Vive Pro Kit" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/HTC-Vive-Pro-Kit.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/HTC-Vive-Pro-Kit-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/HTC-Vive-Pro-Kit-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> Jetpack Aviation has launched a pre-order page for its upcoming Speeder flying motorcycle. Only 20 of these will be available as recreational vehicles, and it is unclear whether they will even be legal to fly anywhere. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-317003" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Speeder.jpg" alt="Speeder" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Speeder.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Speeder-300x202.jpg 300w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Speeder-595x400.jpg 595w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> R700 might seem like a lot to spend on a paper plane, and it is. However, this kit allows you to fly a paper plane remotely from your smartphone, controlling movement with tilt and touch-screen controls. <img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-317005" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/PowerUp-plane.jpg" alt="PowerUp plane" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/PowerUp-plane.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019